<a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0853380/">Julie Taymor</a> was the former director of the infamous <a href="http://spidermanonbroadway.marvel.com/">Spider Man: Turn Off The Dark</a>. You know, the one where all the actors were getting seriously injured. A &#8216;derezzing&#8217; is what happens when you die on the grid. The &#8216;grid&#8217; is the electronic world from the movie TRON. Tron is also a character in the movie TRON, he&#8217;s a program. A &#8216;program&#8217; in TRON is actually a person on the &#8216;grid&#8217;. Is this all making sense?
</div></div></td></tr>
</table>
